🇲🇹 3 Days of Bass Music in the Sun
📅 4th - 6th Sept 2020

Packed with the biggest and best in bassline culture, Rhythm + Waves is opening the doors to an essential summer weekend with a packed lineup of huge names making their way to Malta this September.

Spread across the famed Gianpula Village Malta’s many stages, sights and more (and recognised as one of the best outdoor clubs in the entire Mediterranean) - it’s an unstoppable summer experience held under sunny skies with a who’s who of modern bass music. Across three days and nights, Rhythm + Waves will be delivering a festival experience that everyone will be writing home about. With a lineup packed with non-stop party energy, it’s coming together of friends from around the globe under gorgeous Maltese sunshine

Legends in the game? Look no further than Chase & Status and Andy C, leading the charge for a pumping three day throwdown - with a who’s who of bass music greats joining the party. Rhythm + Waves is the party you thought was never going to happen in 2020, brought to life for an unforgettable weekend.
